                <p class="body-content">The 23-year-old last played for Chelsea on 28 November and has missed the past five matches in all competitions.</p>
                <p class="body-content">He was included in the matchday squad for <a style="text-decoration: none; color:blue;font-weight:bold" href="https://www.chelseafc.com/en" target="_blank">the Blues</a>' win against Aston Villa on 1 December but did not feature.</p>
